# ğŸš€ Monsef â€“ AI-Powered Saudi Family Law Chatbot

![Monsef Logo](https://your-image-link.com/logo.png)

**Monsef** is an AI-powered chatbot designed to help users understand and get guidance on Saudi family law, including marriage, divorce, custody, visitation, Khula, annulment, and maintenance.  

Developed as a **graduation project**, Monsef aims to make legal advice **accessible, clear, and accurate** in Arabic.  

---

## Key Features âœ¨

- **ğŸ§  Advanced AI**: Uses LLMs with RAG for accurate answers.  
- **ğŸ“„ Multi-source processing**: CSV files, legal case CSV, and PDF documents.  
- **ğŸ“š Question classification**: Marriage, divorce, custody, visitation, Khula, annulment, maintenance.  
- **ğŸ“ User intent classification**: Greeting, legal question, clarification request, legal intent, or out-of-scope.  
- **ğŸ’¾ Conversation management**: Save and retrieve chat history via Firebase Firestore.  

---

## Tech Stack ğŸ› ï¸

- **Backend**: Python 3.10+, Flask  
- **AI Models**: OpenAI GPT-4o / GPT Embeddings  
- **Libraries**: LangChain, FAISS, Sentence Transformers / CrossEncoder, pdfplumber  
- **Database**: Firebase Firestore  

