## How it Works âš¡

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[CSV & Legal Cases] --> B[Text Processing]
    C[PDF Files] --> B
    B --> D[Embeddings (OpenAI)]
    D --> E[FAISS Index]
    E --> F[Retrieval + Reranking (CrossEncoder)]
    F --> G[GPT-4o Response Generation]
    G --> H[Conversation Management (Firebase)]
